skdetail:

Invocation Name: holiday maker
des:
Your vacation is important because you have to choose the right one on time and never regret. Therefore, this skill will help your with basic facts about places you would like to visit or those which you wish to.

On your Alexa just ask: Alexa, open holiday maker.

I hope you find the skill suitable for your needs. Further updates are coming.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
